(44, 16, 35, 19, 76, 10, 10, 'Let those men go', 'Wrath and Restraint Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of human actions and their consequences. In Acts, the magistrates'' decision to release Paul and Silas reflects a restraint of wrath, paralleling the idea in Psalms that God restrains the remainder of wrath.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
