(44, 16, 39, 27, 6, 23, 23, 'brought them out', 'Deliverance from Danger', 'This connection highlights the theme of deliverance in both passages. In Acts, the individuals are brought out of the city, while in Daniel, he is taken up out of the den, emphasizing God''s protection in times of peril.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
